# AI Hand Tracking AR

A real-time AI hand tracking and gesture visualization system built using MediaPipe Hands and JavaScript.

## Features
- Real-time hand tracking
- Neon AR effects
- Particle system
- Gesture detection
- Multi-theme interface
- Audio interaction

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- MediaPipe Hands

## How to Run
1. Open the project in a browser.
2. Allow camera access.
3. Click "Enter Experience".

